       <tr>
        <th>
         <p>
          <br>
         </p>
        </th>
        <th>
         <p><strong>Minimum</strong></p>
        </th>
        <th>
         <p><strong>Recommended</strong></p>
        </th>
       </tr>
       <tr>
        <td>
         <p><strong>vCPU</strong></p>
        </td>
        <td>
         <p>2 Cores</p>
        </td>
        <td>
         <p>4 Cores</p>
        </td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
        <td>
         <p><strong>vRAM</strong></p>
        </td>
        <td>
         <p>4 GB</p>
        </td>
        <td>
         <p>8 GB</p>
        </td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
        <td>
         <p><strong>vDISK</strong></p>
        </td>
        <td>
         <p>20 GB</p>
        </td>
        <td>
         <p>160 GB</p>
        </td>
       </tr>
      </tbody>
     </table>
    </div>
   </table-sort>
  </scroll-shadow>
 </table-expand>
</div>
<p>&nbsp;For a redundant deployment, two servers of the same specifications (as mentioned above) are needed.</p>
<h4 id="Software-Prerequisites" style=""><span id="InstallationGuide-SoftwarePrerequisites"></span><strong>Software Prerequisites</strong>
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
  <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cwrfg/4.0/installation-guide#Software-Prerequisites">
