<h4 id="Network-Prerequisites" style=""><span id="InstallationGuide-NetworkPrerequisites"></span><strong>Network Prerequisites</strong>
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
  <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cwrfg/4.0/installation-guide#Network-Prerequisites">
   <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-link copy-headline-link-icon">
    <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#link"></use>
   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h4>
<p>EF Wrapup requires communication with following:</p>
<ul>
 <li>
  <p>&lt;Client Server&gt;</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Cisco Finesse&nbsp;</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Secondary EF Wrapup- only needed for a redundant deployment</p>
 </li>
</ul>
<h4 id="Access-&amp;-Privileges-Requirements" style=""><span id="InstallationGuide-Access&amp;amp;PrivilegesRequirements"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Access &amp; Privileges Requirements</strong>
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
  <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cwrfg/4.0/installation-guide#Access-&amp;amp;-Privileges-Requirements">
   <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-link copy-headline-link-icon">
    <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#link"></use>
   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h4>
<ul>
 <li>
  <p>Administrative access (LocalSystem account or domain administrator) on the WrapUp Server is required to do the installation and configuration.</p>
 </li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="Web-Application-Deployment" style=""><span id="InstallationGuide-WebApplicationDeployment"></span><strong>Web Application Deployment</strong>
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
  <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cwrfg/4.0/installation-guide#Web-Application-Deployment">
   <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-link copy-headline-link-icon">
