   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h3>
<p>
 <br>
</p>
<ol>
 <li>
  <p>Download EF WrapUp web application Installer from <a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1D73b_CQ2Ps9SWxnKmBhPGujTP6PcIfiv" data-scope="external" rel="external noreferrer">Google Drive</a> named<strong> WrapupApp.zip</strong>.</p>
 </li>
</ol>
<p>Open the following location, extract WrapupApp.zip.&nbsp;</p>
<div class="theme-block-image">
 <image-lightbox>
  <div class="block-image" style="--width: 680px" data-component="image" data-align="align-center">
   <img src="/__attachments/a_7f685fcbe52837b43fbb71a24f129315268bafbc2e351e8f1b447b6c6725c809/ig1.png?cb=ae54c849fe4d529d0c6672a209d393ea" alt="ig1.png" data-scope="internal" width="847" height="375">
  </div>
 </image-lightbox>
</div>
<p>
 <br>
 2. Open “WrapupApp” and change in web.config file.
</p>
