 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
  <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cwrfg/4.0/installation-guide#Gadget-Deployment">
   <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-link copy-headline-link-icon">
    <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#link"></use>
   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h2>
<p>Deploy the gadget by following these steps via Filezilla:&nbsp;</p>
<ol>
 <li>
  <p>Install Filezilla client on your machine from which finesse is accessible.&nbsp;</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Download the gadget files from <a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1D73b_CQ2Ps9SWxnKmBhPGujTP6PcIfiv" data-scope="external" rel="external noreferrer">here&nbsp;</a></p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Extract the files at any location&nbsp;</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Change the configuration from <strong>config.js </strong>according to your needs.</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>
   <br>
  </p>
  <ul>
   <li>
    <p>Change the following parameters and set the web service’s server IPs.&nbsp;
     <br>
     <br>
     <span class="theme-inline-image"> <image-lightbox> <span class="inline-image" data-component="inline-image" data-use-text-height="false" style="--height: 400px;"> <img src="/__attachments/a_30d4fb7aa2035c34689c5791520ad04b41296a41dffa3488cabb3467f8843a9f/config.png?cb=c007cd0b2b83c36d6f6d21ac16b1949f" alt="config.png" data-scope="internal"> </span> </image-lightbox> </span></p>
   </li>
   <li>
    <p>Get Not ready reason codes from API. It can be accessed via&nbsp;<a href="https://finessedomain:8445/finesse/api/ReasonCodes?category=NOT_READY." data-scope="external" rel="external noreferrer">https://fdqn:8445/finesse/api/ReasonCodes?category=NOT_READY.</a>&nbsp;Provide credentials for admin to access Reason codes.&nbsp;
     <br>
     From the list of reason codes choose a reason code from uri tag, for example &lt;uri&gt;<span style="--color: #000">/finesse/api/ReasonCode/19</span>&lt;/uri&gt; then in this case code will be 19.
     <br>
     Once you have the reason code, place it in config.js property&nbsp;notReadyReasonCode. So if your reason code is 19 then in config.js you will provide this as&nbsp;notReadyReasonCode : "19".
     <br>
     <br>
     5. Open Filezilla client and connect with finesse server, Add finesse IP in the host, the username should be “3rdpartygadget”, the password you can retrieve/change using putty. Port should be 22
     <br>
     <span class="theme-inline-image"> <image-lightbox> <span class="inline-image" data-component="inline-image" data-use-text-height="false" style="--height: 250px;"> <img src="/__attachments/a_77672f555ae09c6b470d5802ee14bb3f861e9f6a73234b048f5f86f271a031ab/ig13.png?cb=945603fc4628ba757e5e6bc03871c44b" alt="ig13.png" data-scope="internal"> </span> </image-lightbox> </span>
     <br>
     <br>
     6. After successful connectivity with the finesse server you will see the folder “files” highlighted above.
     <br>
     <br>
     7. Create a new folder under file with the name “WrapUpGadget”&nbsp;
     <br>
     <span class="theme-inline-image"> <image-lightbox> <span class="inline-image" data-component="inline-image" data-use-text-height="false" style="--height: 250px;"> <img src="/__attachments/a_77672f555ae09c6b470d5802ee14bb3f861e9f6a73234b048f5f86f271a031ab/ig13.png?cb=945603fc4628ba757e5e6bc03871c44b" alt="ig13.png" data-scope="internal"> </span> </image-lightbox> </span>
     <br>
     <br>
     8. Open the newly created folder and paste all the extracted files into that folder.&nbsp;
     <br>
     <span class="theme-inline-image"> <image-lightbox> <span class="inline-image" data-component="inline-image" data-use-text-height="false" style="--height: 250px;"> <img src="/__attachments/a_2cdf52eddca635eec02c4bb89b5cf7a330ac7f97a71320840433fafbb6b3745d/ig14.png?cb=d7fcb9d97b6c4b960fe4f77c8f202471" alt="ig14.png" data-scope="internal"> </span> </image-lightbox> </span>
     <br>
     <br>
     9. Open finesse cfadmin, go to desktop layout and add “&lt;gadget&gt;/3rdpartygadget/files/WrapUpGadget/WrapupGadget.xml&lt;/gadget&gt;” and save the settings.&nbsp;
     <br>
     <br>
     10. Login the agent, you will see the wrapup gadget here.&nbsp;</p>
   </li>
  </ul>
 </li>
</ol>

